{"tid":1844150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母港豬真係自鳩私，淨係識叫醫護罷工","createTime":"2020-01-26T13:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T16:26:21.000Z","uid":54927,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a98e620d27228c2f436905e9a5468e87454e30ab","tid":1844150,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:38:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老母夠膽就全港大三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5c10d40e62c685238d5d8262fa2967bfc42a1a","tid":1844150,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:39:16.000Z","msg":"返工不了"},{"pid":"e213bdfc60e6fb30dfa7ad91024a74abe0c21390","tid":1844150,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:40:16.000Z","msg":"【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ABcOV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ABcOV7.jpg&h=0f21f561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鑑於中國肺炎疫症嚴峻，港共政府倒行逆施，徹底失去民意信任，已經無力領導現今疫症。<br />\n加上此疫症已經在香港鄰近地區面臨失控下，有機會令香港國家陷入危機，影響香港國家存亡。<br />\n<br />\n為防止中國肺炎在香港大規模爆發，在此宣佈，於香港時間2020年1月26日21時30分正式頒布緊急狀態令<br />\n為免錯過對抗中國肺炎黃金機會，全體連登網民會即時接管香港權力，全力帶領香港國民對抗中國肺炎，以 香港國民福祉為依歸。<br />\n請各位緊記，香港國家一切權力屬於人民，港共政權並非必然行使權力者。<br />\n<br />\n所有重大事件及決策，將會於連登討論區「政事台」討論及表決<br />\n議案帖文將會以【議案】為首以作識別<br />\n<br />\n大多數民意支持，以及正評數量淨值為1000或以上， 該議案會被視作「獲得通過」<br />\n<br />\n正式實現全民參政，全民議政<br />\n議案通過後，將運用全體公民力量及權力，以及民間一切可能的方法實行各種政策 。<br />\n請各位再次緊記，港共政權並非必然行使權力者，權力永遠歸於所有香港國民。<br />\n<br />\n【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844124</a>"},{"pid":"8778e1826b5da2b1f8d55a62462f12c12475f49b","tid":1844150,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T13:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a23141574fc7702d255a8d79c6e0ea14e028791","tid":1844150,"uid":101723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:14:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.29 要罷一齊罷 </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"88d5e7ac458f8bb3077b54c480f2dc4df31f375b","tid":1844150,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a23141574fc7702d255a8d79c6e0ea14e028791","tid":1844150,"uid":101723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:14:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.29 要罷一齊罷 </span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"無問題"},{"pid":"237673cb533483b6b74b1680191e2e39b07f7dd9","tid":1844150,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a23141574fc7702d255a8d79c6e0ea14e028791","tid":1844150,"uid":101723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:14:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.29 要罷一齊罷 </span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}